description: This is the condo you've been looking for! Welcome to 100 Biscayne Drive NW, Unit A3 - a beautifully maintained condominium in the heart of Atlanta. This unit offers a bright, functional layout with an open living & dining area, a well-appointed kitchen fully equipped lots of countertop space & storage.. not to forget the additional coffee bar the owners graciously installed with a waterfall island... providing you ample storage and prep space. Upstairs you'll find large bedrooms, crafted with large windows that bring in natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Off the dining area, you have access to your own private, fenced-in backyard, which is a HUGE plus when buying in the city! Arborgate is a quiet, established community, where residents enjoy access to convenient amenities including a swimming pool, green spaces, and ample parking. The location is unbeatable... minutes to Buckhead, Midtown, Wellstar, Emory & Grady hospitals, major highways, MARTA, Tanyard Creek Park, Bobby Jones Golf Course, Beltline access... and if that's not enough... endless options for dining, shopping, and entertainment right outside your door! If you're looking for a low-maintenance home in the city, this condo is an excellent opportunity to own an AFFORDABLE piece of Atlanta in one of its most desirable locations!
